Priority of Claims
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The proceeds of a bankruptcy are distribute in a particular order of priority:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Administrative expenses (liquidation & bankruptcy expenses, lawyers fees
 on both sides, judge fees).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Unsecured claims arising 
\series bold
after
\series default
 the filing (
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

DIP financing
